title: Tom of the Raiders
creator: Austin Bishop
source: Librivox recording of a public-domain text
description: LibriVox recording of Tom of the Raiders, by Austin Bishop. Read by Brett Downey. Young Adult historical fiction of a young man joining the Union Army and taking part in the Great Locomotive Chase. (Summary by Brett Downey) For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org. M4B format available
subject: librivox; literature; audiobook; adventure; fiction; historical fiction; spy stories; teen/young adult; war stories

reviews.reviewbody: Oh man! That description is terrible. This is a really good book, fast moving, good reader, etc. Good enough I listened twice in 3 days.
